import React from 'react';
import {Dialog, DialogTitle, DialogContent, Typography, Grid, Paper, Button} from '@material-ui/core';

import {makeStyles} from '@material-ui/core/styles';
/*

*/
export default class SMDialogGamePlay extends React.Component {
    render() {
        const dialogStyle = {
            backgroundColor: "black",
        };
        const gridStyle = {
            fontFamily: "Grinched",
            color: "green",
        };
        const btnStyle = {
            fontFamily: "Grinched",
            color: "black",
        };

        return (
        <Dialog onClose={() => this.props.onClick()} fullScreen={true} open={this.props.open}>
            <DialogTitle style={{backgroundColor: '#99ccff'}}>
                <Typography component={'div'} variant="h4" style={gridStyle}>SUPERMATH</Typography>
            </DialogTitle>

            <DialogContent dividers>
            <Grid container justify="space-around" alignItems="center" spacing={5} style={{ backgroundColor: 'orange' }}>
                <Grid item component={Paper} xs={6} sm={6}>
                    <Grid container direction="column" justify="space-around" alignItems="flex-end">
                        <Grid item xs={12}>2</Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12}>+ 2</Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item xs={6} sm={6}>
                        <Grid container justify="center" component={Paper} spacing={3}>
                            <Grid container item direction="row" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start">
                                <Grid item xs={4}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>7</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>8</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>9</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid container item direction="row" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start">
                                <Grid item xs={4}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>4</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>5</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>6</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid container item direction="row" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start">
                                <Grid item xs={4}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>1</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>2</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>3</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid container item direction="row" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start">
                                <Grid item xs={4}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>0</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>+</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4} style={gridStyle}>
                                    <Button size="large">
                                        <Typography variant="h4" style={btnStyle}>-6</Typography>
                                    </Button>
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid container item direction="row" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start" spacing={3}>
                                <Grid item xs={4}><Paper>></Paper></Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4}><Paper>=</Paper></Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={4}><Paper><</Paper></Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                </Grid>

            </Grid>
            </DialogContent>

            <DialogContent dividers>
                QQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQ
            </DialogContent>

        </Dialog>
        );
    }
}
